node.text: Zumba is fun. I've always wanted to try it

Zumbastic! Yes! That's how you feel after a lovely #Zumba workout. Check my stories for few moments of this fun hour.🤩💃
.
It was great fun to groove with @dancewithelly in the Zoom session this evening. I was a part of her energetic sessions when the days were ideal. Thank you, Elly, for the amazing moves and great cardio workout. #notsponsored #notanad
She is an amazing instructor. Always love her sessions. She has other workouts like  KpopX, Cardio Hip Hop and Cardio Blast options too. Go check out her page to register.
.
Lose yourself in the music. Find yourself in good shape, happy space and a relaxed mind.💓
.
